data.description: Second level 2 bedroom 2 bath condo in the conveniently located Vinings View community. Recently renovated marble tiles in kitchen with granite countertops. Open dining/living area with hardwood floors and a balcony. In the hallway, full guest bathroom and laundry closet. Two large bedrooms with big windows. Owner's suite includes a full bathroom and walk in closet. Refinished tubs and fresh paint in both bathrooms and new carpet in both bedrooms. Home warranty with American Home Shield included with purchase (covers appliances, electrical, plumbing and more). Close to Truist Park/The Battery, Cumberland Mall, Vinings Jubilee shopping, I-285, I-75.
